00:15:17,116 --> 00:15:19,151
as an example to the others
of what would happen

436
00:15:19,152 --> 00:15:22,621
if they didn't hurry up and find the treasure...

437
00:15:23,623 --> 00:15:25,390
My father had also written that
even if the treasure were to be found

439
00:15:25,391 --> 00:15:27,492
he would not be able to make it out alive.

440
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:30,462
Did you tell the police about this?

441
00:15:30,463 --> 00:15:35,066
No, I only found out about the letter written
with a needle 20 years later...

443
00:15:36,302 --> 00:15:38,436
And, besides, Renya had already
passed away

445
00:15:38,437 --> 00:15:41,706
and the building was handed over
to someone else...

447
00:15:41,707 --> 00:15:47,712
But, it all, started when I happened
tostalk about this to Ogami 2 years ago...

449
00:15:48,514 --> 00:15:54,352
He went all out and found this place and
started like mad to look for the treasure.

451
00:15:55,021 --> 00:15:58,323
However, he couldn't decipher the code .

452
00:15:58,324 --> 00:16:01,927
He bought this place and had
a large debt because of it.

454
00:16:01,928 --> 00:16:03,895
So, unable to reverse what
had already been done,

456
00:16:03,896 --> 00:16:05,330
he said the following.

457
00:16:05,998 --> 00:16:07,699
Let's gather all the
well-known detectives here

459
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:08,834
and have them decipher the code!

460
00:16:08,835 --> 00:16:12,003
The bait to get all the detectives to come,
is the Thief Kid!

462
00:16:12,004 --> 00:16:14,105
We'll set him up as the host,
and set up a game

464
00:16:14,106 --> 00:16:16,474
which everyone would have
to stake their lives on!

466
00:16:16,943 --> 00:16:19,811
By making it look as though both
you and me have been killed

468
00:16:19,812 --> 00:16:21,079
part way through the game!

469
00:16:23,249 --> 00:16:26,685
Right! Maybe we should
actually kill the maid?

471
00:16:26,686 --> 00:16:29,120
Once they find out that
they really have to be risking their lives

473
00:16:29,121 --> 00:16:31,289
they have no choice but to get serious!

474
00:16:31,290 --> 00:16:35,227
No problem, we'll just put
all the blame on the Thief Kid!"

476
00:16:35,595 --> 00:16:38,496
Which means the one
who chose that maid was.

478
00:16:38,497 --> 00:16:40,131
Mr. Ogami...

479
00:16:40,132 --> 00:16:43,568
He was delighted saying that he found
a maid with a habit just like his

481
00:16:43,569 --> 00:16:45,503
that he could kill,
just as he would be killed

483
00:16:45,504 --> 00:16:50,642
but I guess he never thought that
he'd be killed in the same way.

485
00:16:50,643 --> 00:16:54,212
Yes he bit his nails at that time

486
00:16:54,213 --> 00:16:57,816
because I had recorded
something he had not expected to hear.

488
00:16:57,817 --> 00:17:01,920
Because he was thinking of killing
the maid after the dinner

490
00:17:02,788 --> 00:17:05,190
But, why did you kill Mr. Ogam?

491
00:17:05,191 --> 00:17:08,860
Because I realized that he had found
the location of the hidden treasure

493
00:17:08,861 --> 00:17:12,130
and was planning to kill everyone
including me

495
00:17:12,131 --> 00:17:14,633
By making it look like we all killed
each other using the guns

497
00:17:14,634 --> 00:17:17,335
that he had set up in all of our rooms...

498
00:17:17,837 --> 00:17:19,704
I had no other choice but to carry things
out the way I did, f I were to stop Ogami

500
00:17:19,705 --> 00:17:21,239
who was obsessed like Karasumaru,

501
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:26,912
as well as let the detectives continue
to decipher the code.

503
00:17:27,346 --> 00:17:29,948
The result ended up the same as
40 years ago...

505
00:17:29,949 --> 00:17:31,683
The code could not be deciphered

506
00:17:31,684 --> 00:17:34,085
and the tragedy was repeated

507
00:17:34,220 --> 00:17:37,989
I think your father did decipher
the code, don't you?

509
00:17:40,059 --> 00:17:43,495
Don't you think it's strange that there
is only one clock in this large building

511
00:17:43,496 --> 00:17:45,664
the one in the dining room

512
00:17:46,898 --> 00:17:48,500
the sentence at the top of the code

513
00:17:48,501 --> 00:17:49,301
Iookéd- up at the sky ."

