to take the coin

598
00:20:33,999 --> 00:20:35,666
that was farthest away from you, right?

599
00:20:35,667 --> 00:20:37,001
That's when it flashed through me

600
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:40,271
That you didn't want anyone else
to take the 10 yen coin.

602
00:20:41,307 --> 00:20:44,375
If anyone with cyanide on their hands
touch the 10 yen coin,

604
00:20:44,376 --> 00:20:45,977
redox reaction would occur,

605
00:20:45,978 --> 00:20:47,912
and the whole trick would be disclosed!

606
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:51,449
That's why we all todk you to be the killer

