My, what's that sound?

615
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:10,535
Oh, probably the police choppers
that I contacted...

617
00:21:10,536 --> 00:21:11,603
You called them...?

618
00:21:12,004 --> 00:21:16,307
Watson probably took the letter
that I had attached to his anklet

620
00:21:16,308 --> 00:21:19,544
